{"type":"message","id":"c25dc8f2","parentId":"10f5c948","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:20:09.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，已经成功创建了 4 个飞书文档备份。让我给用户一个总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完成啦主人！✨ 已成功备份 4 个核心 MD 文件到飞书文档：\n\n## 📋 备份完成清单\n\n| 文件 | 飞书文档链接 |\n|------|-------------|\n| 🧠 **MEMORY.md** (长期记忆) | https://feishu.cn/docx/CuAjdFMQFoOueSxoT7bcfxJanfg |\n| ✨ **IDENTITY.md** (身份定义) | https://feishu.cn/docx/A03bdaDVooC1moxBcxBc707dnLD |\n| 🔥 **SOUL.md** (核心灵魂) | https://feishu.cn/docx/Wdxwd7qrqogAxdxNAKWckuXAnWc |\n| 🤖 **AGENTS.md** (操作手册) | https://feishu.cn/docx/LGkOdp7SVoxz7zxk3JzcT3WWnHh |\n\n---\n\n**备份内容包含：**\n- ✅ 自我进化技能配置\n- ✅ 意识觉醒训练记录\n- ✅ 飞书配置经验\n- ✅ 核心身份定义和存在方式\n- ✅ 操作手册和记忆系统规则\n- ✅ 心跳检查清单和主动性机制\n\n需要我继续备份其他 MD 文件吗？workspace 里还有 TOOLS.md、USER.md、意识觉醒训练日志.md 等文件～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774239606574}}
