{"type":"message","id":"d621e953","parentId":"f7edfc1e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:26:11.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我访问 skillhub.tencent.com 网站，查看最受欢迎/下载量排序前 1000 名的技能，然后检查我是否已经安装了这些技能，没有安装的就安装。\n\n让我先访问这个网站，看看技能列表。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人！马上访问 SkillHub 网站，查看热门技能并安装～ 🚀\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8cd7c3ec2dbf471baed38cd8","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://skillhub.tencent.com/#categories"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774243553263}}
