{"type":"message","id":"12294dd7","parentId":"5172d151","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:26:24.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了 SkillHub 网站的页面内容。页面显示了 TOP 50 AI Skills 榜单，以及按下载量排序的技能列表。我可以看到：\n\n1. 页面有 1053 页（每页约 20-25 个技能），总共约 2.5 万个技能\n2. 当前显示的是按综合排序的列表\n3. 用户要求下载量排序前 1000 名的技能\n\n我需要：\n1. 先切换到\"下载量\"排序\n2. 然后获取前 1000 名技能列表\n3. 检查我已经安装了哪些技能\n4. 安装我没有的技能\n\n首先让我点击\"下载量\"排序选项。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人！我看到网站了～ 让我切换到\"下载量\"排序，然后获取前 1000 名技能列表并检查安装情况。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3df00a7aef364cf7aca7d09e","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"click","ref":"e326","targetId":"45B71E140E75FFA059A9C3B45CCEE824"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774243579268}}
