ent\n                - paragraph [ref=e496]: 将AI智能体从任务执行者升级为主动预判需求、持续优化的智能伙伴。集成WAL协议、工作缓冲区、自主定时任务及实战验证模式。Hal Stack核心组件 🦞\n                - generic [ref=e497]:\n                  - generic [ref=e498]:\n                    - img [ref=e499]\n                    - generic [ref=e502]: 11.0 万\n                  - generic [ref=e503]:\n                    - img [ref=e504]\n                    - generic [ref=e506]: \"559\"\n                  - generic [ref=e507]:\n                    - img [ref=e508]\n                    - generic [ref=e512]: v3.1.0\n          - button \"S Skill Vetter AI智能体技能安全预审工具。安装ClawdHub、GitHub等来源技能前，检查风险信号、权限范围及可疑模式。 11.2 万 432 v1.0.0\" [ref=e513] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e514]:\n              - generic [ref=e515]: S\n              - generic [ref=e516]:\n                - generic [ref=e518]: Skill Vetter\n                - paragraph [ref=e519]: AI智能体技能安全预审工具。安装ClawdHub、GitHub等来源技能前，检查风险信号、权限范围及可疑模式。\n                - generic [ref=e520]:\n                  - generic [ref=e521]:\n                    - img [ref=e522]\n                    - generic [ref=e525]: 11.2 万\n                  - generic [ref=e526]:\n                    - img [ref=e527]\n                    - generic [ref=e529]: \"432\"\n                  - generic [ref=e530]:\n                    - img [ref=e531]\n                    - generic [ref=e535]: v1.0.0\n          - button \"W Weather 获取当前天气和预报（无需API密钥） 10.0 万 295 v1.0.0\" [ref=e536] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e537]:\n              - generic [ref=e538]: W\n              - generic [ref=e539]:\n                - generic [ref=e541]: Weather\n                - paragraph [ref=e542]: 获取当前天气和预报（无需API密钥）\n                - generic [ref=e543]:\n                  - generic [ref=e544]:\n                    - img [ref=e545]\n                    - generic [ref=e548]: 10.0 万\n                  - generic [ref=e549]:\n                    - img [ref=e550]\n                    - generic [ref=e552]: \"295\"\n      