        - generic [ref=e1403]:\n                    - img [ref=e1404]\n                    - generic [ref=e1407]: 4.9 万\n                  - generic [ref=e1408]:\n                    - img [ref=e1409]\n                    - generic [ref=e1411]: \"112\"\n                  - generic [ref=e1412]:\n                    - img [ref=e1413]\n                    - generic [ref=e1417]: v1.1.2\n          - button \"S Skill Creator 用于创建有效技能的指南。当用户希望创建新技能（或更新现有技能），以通过专业知识、工作流或工具集成扩展Claude能力时使用。 4.6 万 152 v0.1.0\" [ref=e1418] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e1419]:\n              - generic [ref=e1420]: S\n              - generic [ref=e1421]:\n                - generic [ref=e1423]: Skill Creator\n                - paragraph [ref=e1424]: 用于创建有效技能的指南。当用户希望创建新技能（或更新现有技能），以通过专业知识、工作流或工具集成扩展Claude能力时使用。\n                - generic [ref=e1425]:\n                  - generic [ref=e1426]:\n                    - img [ref=e1427]\n                    - generic [ref=e1430]: 4.6 万\n                  - generic [ref=e1431]:\n                    - img [ref=e1432]\n                    - generic [ref=e1434]: \"152\"\n                  - generic [ref=e1435]:\n                    - img [ref=e1436]\n                    - generic [ref=e1440]: v0.1.0\n          - button \"A Automation Workflows 设计和实施自动化工作流，帮助个体创业者节省时间、扩展业务。适用于识别重复任务、跨工具搭建流程、配置触发器与动作、优化现有自动化等场景。涵盖自动化机会识别、工作流设计、工具选型（Zapier/Make/n8n）、测试与维护。触发词：automate、automation、workflow automation、save time、reduce manual work、automate my business、no-code automation。 4.5 万 182 v0.1.0\" [ref=e1441] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e1442]:\n              - generic [ref=e1443]: A\n              - generic [ref=e1444]:\n                - generic [ref=e1446]: Automation Workflows\n                - paragraph [ref=e1447]: 设计和实施自动化工作流，帮助个体创业者节省时间、扩展业务。适用于识别重复任务、跨工具搭建流程、配置触发器与动作、优化现有自动化等场景。涵盖自动化机会识别、工作流设计、工具选型（Zapier/Make/n8n）、测试与维护。触发词：automate、automation、workflow automation、save time、reduce manual work、automate my business、no-code automation。\n                - generic [ref=e1448]:\n                  - generic [ref=e1449]:\n                    - img [ref=e1450]\n                    - generic [ref=e1453]: 4.5 万\n                  - generic [ref=e1454]:\n                    - img [ref=e1455]\n                    - generic [ref=e1457]: \"182\"\n                  - generic [ref=e1458]:\n                    - img [ref=e1459]\n                    - generic [ref=e1463]: v0.1.0\n        - generic [ref=e1464]:\n          - button [disabled] [ref=e1465]:\n            - img [ref=e1466]\n          - button \"1\" [ref=e1468] [cursor=pointer]\n          - button \"2\" [ref=e1469] [cursor=pointer]\n          - generic [ref=e1470] [cursor=pointer]: ···\n          - button \"1053\" [ref=e1471] [cursor=pointer]\n          - button [ref=e1472] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - img [ref=e1473]\n          - generic [ref=e1475]:\n            - generic [ref=e1476]: 跳至\n            - spinbutton [ref=e1477]: \"1\"\n            - generic [ref=e1478]: 页\n      - generic [ref=e896]:\n        - paragraph [ref=e897]: 关于 SkillHub\n        - heading \"专为中国用户优化的 AI Skills 社区\" [level=2] [ref=e898]\n        - paragraph [ref=e899]: 致谢：衷心感谢每一位 Skill 作者与实践分享者，携手共建国内 AI 生产力生态，共筑创新价值。\n        - generic [ref=e900]:\n          - paragraph [ref=e901]: 【来源声明】本站部分 Skill 技能内容源自互联网或用户上传，相关版权归原作者所有。\n          - paragraph [ref=e902]:\n            - text: 【侵权处理】如涉及版权侵权，请通过邮箱\n            - link \"skillhub_ipr@tencent.com\" [ref=e903] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: mailto:skillhub_ipr@tencent.com\n            - text: 联系我们，我们将及时核实处理。\n    - contentinfo [ref=e904]:\n      - generic [ref=e906]:\n        - paragraph [ref=e907]: Copyright © 2026 SkillHub. 精选 AI Skills 推荐平台。\n        - paragraph [ref=e908]:\n          - text: 技能数据来源于\n          - link \"ClawHub\" [ref=e909] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: https://clawhub.ai\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5f016328f79b306d\">>>"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"F3