{"type":"message","id":"9f19b0db","parentId":"f22281a6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:59:13.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e5722a708f47438d81383e01","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"20ad25e9-a93b-4554-9c04-ac4c8f1f3016\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n  \"name\": \"飞书备份方案持续研究\",\n  \"enabled\": false,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1774139057733,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1774270752667,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"expr\": \"*/10 * * * *\",\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"请研究飞书多维表格（Bitable）备份方案的可行性：\\n\\n## 研究任务\\n\\n1. **分析失败原因**\\n   - 检查 feishu_bitable_create_app API 调用参数\\n   - 尝试不同的参数组合（folder_token、name 等）\\n   - 记录具体错误信息\\n\\n2. **替代方案探索**\\n   - 方案 A：云文档 + 表格块（用 feishu_doc create_table）\\n   - 方案 B：使用现有 Bitable（如果用户已有）\\n   - 方案 C：云盘文件备份（JSON 原始数据）\\n\\n3. **实践测试**\\n   - 尝试用 feishu_doc 在文档中创建表格\\n   - 测试表格内容写入\\n   - 验证是否可实现类似 Bitable 的结构化存储\\n\\n4. **输出报告**\\n   - 哪种方案最可行？\\n   - 需要什么额外权限？\\n   - 推荐什么备份策略？\\n\\n## 记录要求\\n\\n写入文件：`memory/飞书备份研究日志.md`\\n- 研究时间\\n- 尝试的方法\\n- 成功/失败\\n- 下一步计划\\n\\n记住：目标是找到可靠的飞书备份方案，不一定要用 Bitable！\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"to\": \"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774268591479,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 93791,\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"20ad25e9-a93b-4554-9c04-ac4c8f1f3016","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"飞书备份方案持续研究","enabled":false,"createdAtMs":1774139057733,"updatedAtMs":1774270752667,"schedule":{"expr":"*/10 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"n