{"type":"message","id":"42196ea6","parentId":"bcccd307","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:41:51.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！飞书权限里有日历相关的权限：\n- calendar:calendar:read\n- calendar:calendar.event:update\n- calendar:calendar.event:delete\n- calendar:calendar.event:read\n- calendar:calendar.event:create\n- calendar:calendar.free_busy:read\n- calendar:calendar.event:reply\n\n所以我可以创建日历事件！但是飞书插件的 tools 里没有直接的日历创建命令。让我用 exec 调用飞书 API 或者用 message 工具发送一个待办到飞书。\n\n实际上，最简单的方式是使用飞书任务（task）API，因为权限里有 task:task:write。\n\n让我尝试创建一个飞书任务。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！✅ 飞书权限已包含日历和任务权限！\n\n让我创建这个待办事项到飞书任务：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7427785d88b240e890584df2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$body = @{ title = \"写总结\"; description = \"明天早上 9 点写总结\"; due_date = (Get-Date \"2026-03-24T09:00:00+08:00\").ToString(\"o\") } | ConvertTo-Json; Write-Host $body 2>&1","yieldMs":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774273305151}}
